# AEO / llms.txt

When editing **site copy**, **SEO meta** (`src/data/seo-content.ts`), or **CTA URLs** (`src/data/content.ts` `ctaContent`), read **`public/llms.txt`** first. It lists authoritative booking and LinkedIn URLs, impact stats as shown on the site, and citation rules.

After changing any of those facts, **update `public/llms.txt`** so it stays in sync (especially calendar URL, LinkedIn URL, and impact numbers). Do not invent credentials, employers, or metrics not present in `content.ts` or on-page copy.
